message.content: The paper "Vqabq Visual Question Answering By Basic Questions" most likely belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), as it deals with the task of answering questions about images. Other likely sub-categories could include "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) and "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), as the paper also involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) could also be possible sub-categories, but are less likely as they are not as directly related to the task of visual question answering.
